Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.70,0:15:55.22,miao,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(79,135)\fs21\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\fr270\fad(495,0)}迷人的先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道这附近有没有哪家店的茶比较好喝的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:15:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 有一家店不错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.39,0:16:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.82,0:16:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.38,0:16:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 请务必带我去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.00,0:16:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.72,0:16:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:10.74,miao,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(163,82)\fs24\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\fr270}想着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:10.74,miao,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(105,155)\fs24\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\fr270}他是从哪里来的呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.82,0:16:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬社长 走…吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.76,0:16:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这身奇怪的打扮是要干嘛啊…亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.29,0:16:26.72,miao,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(501,99)\fs24\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\fr270}真实身份
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.29,0:16:26.72,miao,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(437,160)\fs24\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\fr270}果然是绝不可以泄漏的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:14.81,miao,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(306,176,243,176)\fs24\fr23}专\N门\N对\N付
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:14.81,miao,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(300,289,236,289)\fs24\fr23}英\N雄\N的\N邪\N恶\N组\N织\N! ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.81,0:17:18.31,miao,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(433,203,369,203)\fs24\fr-14}或\N是\N凶\N恶\N的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.81,0:17:18.31,miao,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(374,207,310,207)\fs24\fr-14}宇\N宙\N怪\N人\N! ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.31,0:17:21.81,miao,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(356,123,292,123)\fs24\fr-29}还是说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.31,0:17:21.81,miao,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(395,211,331,211)\fs24\fr-29}是谜样的小猫猎人! ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.88,0:17:26.45,miao,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,60)\fs50\3c&HFF8080&\bord1}大危机!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.67,0:17:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛社长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.02,0:17:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧？亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.55,0:18:01.02,miao,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(542,140)\fs25\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\fr270}我并不是你所说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.55,0:18:01.02,miao,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(484,108)\fs25\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\fr270}的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.03,0:18:15.53,miao,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(571,108)\fs21\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\fr270}心得之
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.03,0:18:15.53,miao,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(525,117)\fs21\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\fr270}身为英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.27,0:18:21.50,miao,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(510,135)\fs21\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\fr270}绝不可以失去希望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.14,0:19:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.21,0:19:15.03,miao,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(145,147)\fs21\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\fr270}我…我不是你说的那个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.43,0:19:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说 你是要帮我忙吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.54,0:19:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.54,0:19:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才参加那边的马戏团表演时
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.86,0:19:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一不小心就让球散得一地都是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.66,0:19:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是帮了我大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.00,0:19:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧 亚利亚社长？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.47,0:19:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？这只猫是怎么搞的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.64,0:19:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错 不错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.10,0:19:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 在那边保持平衡站好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.65,0:19:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.64,0:19:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.15,0:20:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚利亚社长真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.30,0:20:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把球捡回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.50,0:20:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 全捡了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.23,0:20:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那就再试一次看看吧 不要输给那只猫了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.22,0:20:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.16,0:21:09.41,miao,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(516,124)\fs22\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\fr270\fad(0,1200)}把人偶弄脏了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.17,0:21:11.57,miao,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(255,60)\fs40\t(0,1356,1,\fs30)}不及格的英雄! !
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.02,0:21:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要 小健
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.85,0:21:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没办法啊 掉到哪里去了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.02,0:21:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道 我要去找啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.24,0:21:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 不要去了 已经这么晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.71,0:21:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小健
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.20,0:21:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小健回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.30,0:21:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁帮忙拿回来的呢？而且…变得好脏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.04,0:21:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 就算脏也没关系 小健回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.10,0:21:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是神把他带回来的 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.25,0:21:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小健 我不会再丢下你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.85,0:22:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.95,0:22:12.20,miao,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(576,193)\fs20\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\fr270\fad(450,1400)}那一天的夕阳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.74,0:22:12.20,miao,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(90,234)\fs18\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\fr270\fad(660,1400)}感觉是在所有的夕阳之中 ——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.11,0:22:18.61,miao,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(186,239)\fs18\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\fr270\fad(300,0)}看起来最耀眼的。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.37,0:22:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来 亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.47,0:22:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里 说不定亚利亚社长真的是个英雄哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.55,0:22:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.96,0:22:45.60,miao,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(431,329)\fs35\c&H50F654&\fad(1350,0)}那位 帅气的英雄啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.96,0:22:45.60,miao,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(477,473)\fs30\fad(1350,0)}结束
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.92,0:24:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想见 好想见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.18,0:24:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想见到她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.74,0:24:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个快一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.35,0:24:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要先走一步了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.60,0:24:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.79,0:24:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.57,0:24:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位 星星一般的精灵…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.22,0:24:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们一起度过美好的时光吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OPJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.76,0:00:46.65,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}頬をなでる 優しい風
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.39,0:00:55.82,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}波音に 揺られて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.16,0:01:05.43,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}体の中 ほどけてゆくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.01,0:01:16.19,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}目を閉じて 見えてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.80,0:01:24.45,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}風の行く道が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.69,0:01:34.55,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}さあ 漕ぎ出そう 光る波へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.87,0:01:43.71,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}笑顏が すぐ こぼれる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.07,0:01:53.87,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}ねえ 伝えよう このときめき
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.17,0:02:04.47,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}風にのって あなたのもとへ 行くわ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.69,0:02:08.67,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}ウンディーネ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OPCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.76,0:00:46.65,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}轻拂面颊的 温柔的风
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.39,0:00:55.82,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}在海浪的歌声中摇曳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.16,0:01:05.43,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}慢慢地 融入身体里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.01,0:01:16.19,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}闭上双眼 看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.80,0:01:24.45,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}是风的轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.69,0:01:34.55,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}来 让我们出发 向着闪亮的波涛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.87,0:01:43.71,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}脸上的笑容 从未消失
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.07,0:01:53.87,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}快 传达到彼方 把这份感动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.17,0:02:04.47,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}托付给清风 带到你的身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.69,0:02:08.67,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}水之精灵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【EDJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.78,0:22:49.51,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}水辺に映る いつもの景色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.19,0:22:57.08,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}穏やかに 流れる時間と
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.28,0:23:00.77,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}移りゆく 季節の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.24,0:23:08.78,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}見つけたの 変わらぬ想いを
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.12,0:23:13.09,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}聴いて 幸せの歌は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.36,0:23:19.71,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}そう いつでも 心の中あふれて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.76,0:23:28.28,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}描いてた夢 叶えられるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.63,0:23:31.56,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}いつかは オーバー ザ レインボー
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.68,0:23:39.47,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}雨上がりの虹 見上げた空に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.82,0:23:45.26,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}はばたいて いつか 青い鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.54,0:23:53.68,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}胸いっぱいの愛を 集めてよ きっとレインボー
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.07,0:24:00.31,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}心にはいつも愛を 越えてくわ きっとレインボー
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【EDCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.78,0:22:49.51,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}不变的景色 倒映在水边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.19,0:22:57.08,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}在缓缓流逝的时光和
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.28,0:23:00.77,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}不断变化的季节中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.24,0:23:08.78,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}寻觅到 那不变的想念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.12,0:23:13.09,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}听 那幸福的歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.36,0:23:19.71,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}像这样 一直 满溢于心中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.76,0:23:28.28,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}所有的梦想 都将实现
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.63,0:23:31.56,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}我们 总会越过彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.68,0:23:39.47,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}雨后的彩虹 清澄的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.82,0:23:45.26,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}相信那青鸟 总会展翅飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.54,0:23:53.68,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}收集起胸中的爱意 定会见到彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.07,0:24:00.31,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}心中常怀爱意 定能越过彩虹


